{"tid":1511264,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[自我進化]每日十點嗌口號 可以同時嗌埋活動日程","createTime":"2019-08-27T13:09:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T13:42:39.000Z","uid":269515,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a402bc2c8eb165fe4269dd2e10ee94ca521f13b6","tid":1511264,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:09:49.000Z","msg":"呢排見到愈來愈多巴絲加入十點一齊嗌口號，但都見有巴絲會反思嗌口號嘅目的其實係啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n既然係咁，其實我地不妨再自我進化，試下嗌完口號後再嗌埋活動日程希望多啲人留意呢星期有乜活動！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以如常都係光復香港開頭，確定有一定數量嘅手足join，口號都嗌完一輪之後，帶頭嘅巴絲可以自己嗌全句，其他人再跟住嗌：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>八二八！ 遮打見！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n八三一！遮打見！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n九月一！機場見！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n九月二！三罷！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果怕太多記唔晒嘅可以先嗌最近嘅兩個活動都可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然大家嗌之餘都要注意安全，喺街嘅手足keep住走位，留意下有冇唔友善嘅廢中廢老接近自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n祝大家一呼百應！<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光復香港 <br />\n時代革命！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BiNQxxV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBiNQxxV.jpg&h=21c16fd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LgdcLSU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLgdcLSU.jpg&h=7d8fce73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bUxUeMg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbUxUeMg.jpg&h=c53a7f94&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76b4fc57b9f3f0d6ed21b21b14f108263616451f","tid":1511264,"uid":2612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:10:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h89LSSA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh89LSSA.gif&h=778b9ffb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e5affac8171879e59e2ff4a1e2bb4717f8c680dc","tid":1511264,"uid":258208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76b4fc57b9f3f0d6ed21b21b14f108263616451f","tid":1511264,"uid":2612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:10:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h89LSSA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh89LSSA.gif&h=778b9ffb&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:11:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"855171115f35964439872d5076b2b155134b727f","tid":1511264,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a402bc2c8eb165fe4269dd2e10ee94ca521f13b6","tid":1511264,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:09:49.000Z","msg":"呢排見到愈來愈多巴絲加入十點一齊嗌口號，但都見有巴絲會反思嗌口號嘅目的其實係啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n既然係咁，其實我地不妨再自我進化，試下嗌完口號後再嗌埋活動日程希望多啲人留意呢星期有乜活動！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以如常都係光復香港開頭，確定有一定數量嘅手足join，口號都嗌完一輪之後，帶頭嘅巴絲可以自己嗌全句，其他人再跟住嗌：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>八二八！ 遮打見！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n八三一！遮打見！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n九月一！機場見！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n九